# Google Drive Picker (Phase F) — public, non-secret client config.
#
# These are read at build time via import.meta.env and embedded in the client
# bundle. That's expected and safe: the OAuth client_id is public by design, and
# the API key is restricted to your origins + to the Picker/Drive APIs in the
# Google Cloud console. No private secret lives here.
#
# Setup: create both values in Google Cloud (see the Phase F setup steps), then
# copy this file to `.env` (gitignored) and fill them in. Restart `npm run dev`
# and re-run `npm run build` so the new values are picked up.

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
